ttp://dbpedia.org/resource/Cedi_Osman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most talented addition\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Osman was a genuine rotation-level player in the NBA last season, he expected to sign an NBA deal this summer, and so did other NBA teams, and then the market dried up and Panathinaikos became the best option.\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3341, \"end\": 3346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cedi_Osman\", \"score\": 0.9999999937599569, \"rank\": 3.462540889151809e-09, \"text\": \"Osman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cedi_Osman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cedi_Osman\"}, {\"begin\": 3390, \"end\": 3393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4721686062023245e-31, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 3430, \"end\": 3433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4721686062023245e-31, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 3469, \"end\": 3472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4721686062023245e-31, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 3513, \"end\": 3526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panathinaikos_B.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.696692129115621e-29, \"text\": \"Panathinaikos\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panathinaikos_B.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panathinaikos_B.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a genuine rotation-level player\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3382}, {\"ngram\": \"the market\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"the best option\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For as good as Dinos Mitoglou and Marius Grigonis were last season, there is no denying Osman is an upgrade on both.\\u00c2 Lorenzo Brown rounds out what is now a star-studded guard rotation: Kostas Sloukas, Kendrick Nunn, Jerian Grant, and Brown.\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3566, \"end\": 3580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dinos_Mitoglou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dinos Mitoglou\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dinos_Mitoglou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dinos_Mitoglou\"}, {\"begin\": 3585, \"end\": 3600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marius_Grigonis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marius Grigonis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marius_Grigonis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marius_Grigonis\"}, {\"begin\": 3639, \"end\": 3644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cedi_Osman\", \"score\": 0.9999999937599569, \"rank\": 3.462540889151809e-09, \"text\": \"Osman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cedi_Osman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cedi_Osman\"}, {\"begin\": 3670, \"end\": 3683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorenzo Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://d